door.de/Jobs/FINatycs-GmbH-Jobs-E4866343.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eFINatycs GmbH\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/Sunday-Natural-Products-GmbH-Jobs-E2435996.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eSunday Natural Products GmbH\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/Almedia-Jobs-E8716600.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eAlmedia\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/SRH-University-Jobs-E644893.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eSRH University\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/Riverty-Group-GmbH-Jobs-E4392908.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eRiverty Group GmbH\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/Ottobock-SE-and-Co-KGaA-Jobs-E717221.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eOttobock SE \\u0026 Co. KGaA\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/Hologic-Jobs-E1568.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eHologic\\u003c/a\\u003e, \\u003ca href=\\\\\\\"https://www.glassdoor.de/Jobs/OSRAM-GmbH-Jobs-E10648.htm\\\\\\\"\\u003eOSRAM GmbH\\u003c/a\\u003e\\\"}}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"77:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$79\\\"}}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"7a:T176b,\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"\\u003cdiv\\u003e\\u003ch4 class=\\\"jobSectionHeader\\\"\\u003e\\u003cb\\u003eYour mission\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/h4\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\n\\nAs a \\u003cb\\u003eUI/UX Product Designer\\u003c/b\\u003e at NeuroNation, you will take ownership of our flagship Brain-Training app, crafting engaging and intuitive user experiences for millions worldwide. Working closely with cross-functional teams, you\\u0026rsquo;ll blend creativity, research, and data-driven insights to design features that boost growth, engagement, and long-term user value.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\nKey Responsibilities\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\nImprove and maintain our mobile Brain-Training application to drive user growth, retention, and revenue\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nConceptualize, validate and implement new product features\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nIdentify trends and market-specific needs to ensure we offer the highest value to our users\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nDefine and uphold our UI \\u0026amp; visual standards\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nRun deep analysis on user's behavior, identify patterns and provide solutions\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nLive with a Growth mindset \\u0026ndash; you constantly look for learning opportunities for yourself and the team\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nActively ensure the quality of your product\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nWork closely with the Marketing, Business Intelligence, Customer Care and CRM Departments\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nBecome the expert of your product\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nBe part of the Growth and Product Teams\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003ch4 class=\\\"jobSectionHeader\\\"\\u003e\\u003cb\\u003e\\n\\nYour profile\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/h4\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\n\\nMust-have Skills:\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\nAt least 5 years of Mobile App Design experience in a product team delivering digital consumer-facing products (E-commerce, Games, or ideally Education/Health)\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nPersonal interest in self-improvement\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nExperience designing (partially or fully) B2C mobile applications available on the Play or App Stores\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nLocated in Germany, preferably Berlin, and able to come to the office once a month (sponsored)\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nProficient in design tools such as Figma, Sketch, Adobe Creative Suite, and prototyping tools\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nExcellent eye for visual design and details\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nExperience conducting or supporting UX research to develop or improve digital products\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nAcademic background in Design, Business Administration, Neuroscience, Psychology, or a related field\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nLifelong learner, regularly engaging with science, health, and productivity content\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nStrong organizational and project management skills, able to handle multiple projects concurrently\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nAbility to analyze user flows, engagement, retention, and relevant data\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nTeam-player mindset, eager to support colleagues\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nMotivation to be part of a start-up that positively impacts people\\u0026rsquo;s lives\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\nNice-to-have Skills:\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nFamiliarity with Google Material Design 3 and Apple Liquid Glass design guidelines\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nKnowledge of Lean Startup, Design Sprints, and Growth Hacking\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nBasic knowledge of German, French, Spanish, or Italian\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003ch4 class=\\\"jobSectionHeader\\\"\\u003e\\u003cb\\u003e\\n\\nWhy us?\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/h4\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cul\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\n\\nWork on something that \\u003cb\\u003etruly creates value for people\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nMake a \\u003cb\\u003esignificant impact on a platform used by millions worldwide\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nTake on \\u003cb\\u003emeaningful, exciting projects\\u003c/b\\u003e instead of routine corporate or agency work\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nHelp \\u003cb\\u003erevolutionize health and education systems\\u003c/b\\u003e through technology and innovation\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nEnjoy \\u003cb\\u003eflexible working hours\\u003c/b\\u003e (core hours: 9:30\\u0026ndash;16:30 CET)\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nReceive a \\u003cb\\u003eBVG ticket\\u003c/b\\u003e to support sustainable and convenient commuting\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nAccess an \\u003cb\\u003eUrban Sports Club membership\\u003c/b\\u003e for your well-being and work-life balance\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003cli\\u003e\\nBe part of an \\u003cb\\u003eopen, supportive culture\\u003c/b\\u003e that values learning, growth, and collaboration\\u003c/li\\u003e\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003ch4 class=\\\"jobSectionHeader\\\"\\u003e\\u003cb\\u003e\\n\\nAbout us\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003c/h4\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\n\\nNeuroNation is a digital health company with the mission to help millions of people to regain, maintain, and improve cognitive and mental health.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\nSupported by the Ministry of Research in several projects, awarded with the AOK-Leonardo - a digital prevention award funded by the Ministry of Health - we have the required resources and products to pursue our mission, together with clinicians and researchers worldwide.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cb\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\nWhy You Should Join NeuroNation\\u003c/b\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\nAt NeuroNation, we're not just creating products; we're making a real difference in people's lives. Our mission to revolutionise cognitive health through science-based brain training means that every challenge we design and every feature we develop has a purpose. We aim to help individuals live healthier, more fulfilling lives.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cb\\u003eImpactful Work:\\u003c/b\\u003e Working with us means contributing to a product that profoundly impacts cognitive health. Our brain training programs, backed by cutting-edge neuroscience and cognitive psychology, are designed to enhance cognitive functions, improve working memory, and elevate our users' quality of life.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cb\\u003eInspiring Environment: \\u003c/b\\u003eAt NeuroNation, you'll join a vibrant team of passionate and innovative professionals. We believe that collaboration and creativity thrive in a fun and inclusive environment. From team-building activities to spontaneous brainstorming sessions, we make sure that work is both productive and enjoyable.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cb\\u003eWork Wherever You Thrive:\\u003c/b\\u003e While our headquarters is in Berlin, Germany, and our team is spread across Europe, we want everyone to work where they feel most productive. If you're based in Berlin, we warmly encourage you to join us in the office to collaborate and connect in person. If you're not in Berlin, feel free to work remotely\\u0026mdash;from one of our offices, a co-working space, or your home\\u0026mdash;anywhere within \\u0026plusmn;2 hours of Berlin (CET).\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\nWith all our tools in the cloud and weekly video catch-ups, you\\u0026rsquo;ll stay connected, supported, and productive no matter where you are.\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\n\\u003cb\\u003eFlexible hours: \\u003c/b\\u003eOur flexible working hours and remote work policy let you tailor your work schedule to fit your lifestyle, ensuring you can perform at your best.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\u003c/div\\u003e\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"7b:T6cd,\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"https://de.indeed.com/rc/gd/png?a=6JcVF1zuFenUUSk6hkqeQ3wFVDaBrQiiwhsUnPcYFQhx8ZpyNE5fVR3pvP3Jyy96vFvE5JDsIuWgcuKWqWeuewA1R9UGaNYIfMw3AJJN6J71-bVaIMix6AySm4jTgdB35FqtQnzW8hYhsGEY3l4VVC3qxeVnoJtSd7IElrTE322xy3_aEKg9d_OgMN3NmiaFvn6XVP0GvkkPMnNzCaz9Qmz3QS6kzWAc5C8_Gx7a8ismJLj3ax8xDfeGnyo-OeBVcNk8MU2u-3Kb7Chy5zPOI2Yuz2uQuVwxTZVryjo0C6h3jSS8zvhysSYp-h9LtMP7dMrs1eFfrm_2Q2BDNukwFYE11LJoK0A0_F4V8jS8Cr4oavo6jbYcC3SR5lMT4EGs3PcMvPvsdNwmbqjbg2qAbDCmR044Uhoad40kvM74crH8FevS60tVxCMZOUk